’Ů@dc0d93c653b69a2c534faf74cb1ea56461d51aeba943056497829ea5f5f775e2ŮśTitle: title: job kill
Path: Examples
Content:
Kill a newly spawned job.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> let id = job spawn { sleep 10sec }; job kill $id


```
